folder: Central Park West & 106th Street (West), Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Park West, at West 106th Street. Also shown is West 106th Street, west from and including Central Park West. Building shown on the left, is the General Memorial Hospital. Note the Ninth Ave., Elevated on
Columbus Ave.
December 8, 1916.
E. Mason.
title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 106th Street (West)

Central Park West, 107th to 106th Streets. (Before R'.
construction).
President Borough of Manhatten.
March 22, 1920
title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 106th Street

folder: Central Park West & 106th Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Parl West, west side, from 106th to 107th Streets. In the left may be seen a portion of the General Memorial Hospital. Note the condition of the street, due to excavation work on the
Eighth Avenue subway.
July 10, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
